    "Contrarily, viral pneumonia (right image) manifests a more diffuse \"interstitial\" pattern, involving both lungs.By carefully curating and annotating this new dataset, we aim to enhance the accuracy and robustness of our AI system's performance for pneumonia classification using chest X-ray images.",
    "MethodsIn this study, we utilize a dataset comprising of 1,583 normal (non-pneumonia) images and 4,273 pneumonia images for pneumonia detection.",
    "The ensuing discussion will delve into the dataset's specifics, the deep learning techniques adopted, and the models employed.",
    "Initially, an enhanced model was deployed for pneumonia classification, followed by the application of a CNN architecture to yield obtain the classification results.",
